cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on video generation tasks and proposes a novel algorithm to improve temporal coherence. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of adversarial training and proposes a new learning objective. 
3. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with video super-resolution and unpaired video translation. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new algorithm for improving the performance of GAN-based video generation tasks. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is also a possible category as the paper deals with generating visually coherent videos.
